# Settings
Install npm

# Install yeoman
npm install -g yo

# Start scaffolding
yo angular

# Install grunt cli
npm install -g grunt-cli

# Install grunt
npm install grunt -g

(some version you need to do this)
npm install grunt --save-dev

# Install karma if failed previously (or just uncomment karma test in your Gruntfile.js)
npm install grunt-karma karma karma-phantomjs-launcher karma-jasmine jasmine-core phantomjs phantomjs-prebuilt --save-dev

# Install cli for karma
npm install -g karma-cli

karma init

Generate bower components (angular,bootstrap,etc)
bower install

wiredep
inject bower components into your project

# Build & run
grunt build
grunt serve

# Other nice stuff
bower install gsap --save

# Search for packages
bower search xx

# uncss, remove unneeded css 
npm install grunt-uncss
uncss http://url > mini.css


# FAQ
## When doing 'grunt', Fatal error: Unable to find local grunt.
npm install - Install dependencies

Error: Cannot find module 'karma'
url:https://github.com/yeoman/generator-angular/issues/1239

Edit the dependency in /usr/local/lib/node_modules/yo/package.json to be "yeoman-environment": "1.4.0"
cd /usr/local/lib/node_modules/yo
rm -rf node_modules (run from the yo directory)
npm install (run from the yo directory)





npm install bower??
